3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training and comparing different models. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses neural networks to make predictions. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper involves measuring human perception and comparing it to model predictions.
